data.description: Beautifully maintained 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom townhome in Littleton. This home has a storybook exterior and no shortage of living space! The bright open floor plan has vaulted ceilings with beautiful hardwood floors stretch that throughout the main living area. Cozy up to the beautiful stone fireplace with custom mantle that is the centerpiece of the living room. The kitchen features granite countertops, recessed lighting and ample cabinet space offering storage solutions at every turn and sliding glass doors that lead to the outdoor patio. The upstairs master retreat is the perfect place to relax after a long day. Complete with double vanity, large soaker tub with separate shower, bay window seating and a spacious walk-in closet. The unfinished basement is perfect for making your own. Quiet neighborhood with a wealth of nearby amenities. The convenient location is perfect for commuting with and close to public transportation. Schedule your private showing today!
